tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ExperimentResults
(
    ExperimentID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ExperimentName VARCHAR(255),
    VariableTested VARCHAR(255),
    OutcomeObserved VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  experiment_date DATE,
  variable_tested TEXT,
  outcome_observed TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE experiments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_name VARCHAR(255),
    experiment_date DATE,
    experimenter VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE experiment_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id INT,
    variable_id INT,
    outcome_id INT,
    result_value FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (experiment_id) REFERENCES experiments(experiment_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (variable_id) REFERENCES experiment_variables(variable_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (outcome_id) REFERENCES experiment_outcomes(outcome_id)
);
